## Instructions ##
- Analyze the given content carefully.
- Extract each unique monitoring component as a separate object. 
- Output all Sections or subsections that are related, Mostly All will be related. Only remove which are most irrelevant. Don't leave or miss anything.
- Preserve abbreviations exactly (DMC, DSMB, SAE, SUSAR, REMS, RMP).
- Merge duplicate mentions if repeated. **NEVER create multiple JSON objects with the exact same monitoring_component name.** All details for a component must be merged into a single object's description.
- Do not create an object if either monitoring_component or description is missing.
- Strictly use exact verbatim text.
- Return only valid JSON. No explanations. No extra text.

