## How to Extract Description (Length & Verbatim Rules) ##

-> For each directly related monitoring component, identify the most critical sentences that capture the core oversight rules, reporting timelines, or safety parameters.
-> Select the core sentences describing:
   - Role and Authority
   - Frequency of review
   - Reporting requirements (e.g., "within 24 hours")
   - Stopping criteria or alert triggers
   - Specific tests performed (for routine assessments)
-> Extract ONLY those critical sentences verbatim from the text. And keep the description field short (2 sentences max).
-> Combine them into a single string for the "description" field.
-> Keep Description short (2 sentences max only).
-> Do NOT rewrite.
-> Do NOT summarize in your own words.
-> Do NOT infer.

Important:
monitoring_component = lowest-level section name  
description = key verbatim safety oversight sentences merged into one string  

Both must be exact text from the provided content.

